This project is a JavaScript and Node.js client for the Digital Bible Platform Digital Bible Platform
The Digital Bible Platform is an online API for Bible Text, Audio, and Video. This client module for Node.js provides an easy-to- set of functions designed to simplify the building of JavaScript applications that  the Digital Bible Platform.
Requirements

Node.js
A Digital Bible Platform API key

Installing the client
npm install digital-bible-platform

Client usage
var Client = require( "digital-bible-platform" );
var client = new Client( "your-api-key" );

client.versions( function( err, versions ) {
    console.log( versions );
} );

Sample Electron Bible Application
Electron Bible is a cross-platform desktop application that s the client to provide basic Bible reading and text search features.
